<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id05f20050-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—<ref href="/us/pl/104/295">Pub. L. 104–295</ref> amended directory language of <ref href="/us/pl/103/182">Pub. L. 103–182</ref>. See 1993 Amendment note below.</p>
